Tya Janè Ramey (amuru Disemba 25, 1997 na Port of Spain) bu ihe nlere anya na eze nwanyi mara mma sitere na Trinidad and Tobago, onye meriri akwukwo Miss Universe Trinidad and Tobago 2022
Ọ ga-anọchi anya obodo ya na Miss Universe 2022.
Ọ bụbu onye mmeri nke Miss World Trinidad and Tobago, Miss World Caribbean na Top 40 semifinal na Miss World na 2019.
